data.description: LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION- A rare find in Brookside Village! Fantastic property to build your dream home on. Superb school district Zoned to Glenda Dawson High School. This is a must see!    Selling "as is" 2.2 acres (property value only): with 100+year old oak trees, ball cypress, pecan,magnolia,maple pine and other trees. Pond has enclosed fencing.    House is 960 sq. ft,.2 bed- 1 bath. all electric, water well(separately feeds house and pond) leech field septic system, washer/dryer, refrigerator,(w/ ice maker) stove and microwave.    Groomed acreage. 1/4 acre stocked pond with large mouth bass, perch, established ecosystem with bullfrogs, crawfish and at least 10 species of waterfowl.  Current owners are members of Audubon and have recorded 50 bird species sightings on property including Kingfisher resident. 40+ migrating ducks that stay throughout the winter.    Storage unit included.
